			<p>In body text, write out numbers from one to nine; use figures from 10 upwards</p>

			<p>Never start a sentence or title with a figure. If a sentence or title begins with a number, it must be spelt out. Numbers between twenty-one and ninety-nine, when written in words, should be hyphenated</p>

